channel.title: Comments on: Joke Shake App Review

item.title: By: Charles McKeever
item.dc:creator: Charles McKeever
item.description: Dean Murphy is getting ready to launch a new app called Number Tap. It's a math based game with some pretty sweet UI elements. His menus are playful and organic feeling, which is the opposite of how I think of math, so I'm looking forward to seeing it in on the Apple App Store.
